{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 19782, "create_time": 1640953223, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "这就是费拉\n由于我幼儿园、小学教师们并没有文化，因此我完全可以不把他们当回事", "timestamp": 1640953223}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 19783, "create_time": 1640953820, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 虽然我知道小学老师中学老师也就大专师范，但是整人的手段真的恶心。估计师范大学就教怎么恶心学生了", "timestamp": 1640953820}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 19784, "create_time": 1640954027, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re 洞主: 这不是某一个老师某一个地方的错，这是整个国家教育的畸形，人心的恶毒凶残", "timestamp": 1640954027}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 19785, "create_time": 1640954498, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "想到教师我首先想到的是词是责任，教师担负塑造无数学生人格的责任。但是现实中提到最多的词是教师的底线，师德，好像教师不做伤天害理就是很高要求了", "timestamp": 1640954498}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 19786, "create_time": 1640954719, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "夜深忽梦少年事了属于是\n不过在这种情况下我从来没有跟着起哄 反正我有的是时间", "timestamp": 1640954719}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 19787, "create_time": 1640954822, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "这可以说是“有权不用过期作废”的劣化版，在我所在的农村地区老师还是有约束的，毕竟以后还要见面，其中老年教师甚至可能是当地的体面人，但如果是在原子人地区，那就真是“有权不用过期作废”了", "timestamp": 1640954822}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 19788, "create_time": 1640954906, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "至于校长，则一般应该是忙于贪污的，遇到这种事情不会想理，只会想办法和稀泥", "timestamp": 1640954906}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 19789, "create_time": 1640955210, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "高中班主任最喜欢抓典型批斗，搁两三天就抓几个不满意的学生在班级里公开批斗羞辱打骂，杀鸡儆猴万马齐喑。我就经常被批斗，找家长写反思做保证公开检讨，一套一套的", "timestamp": 1640955210}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 19794, "create_time": 1640955456, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 你干了什么坏事？", "timestamp": 1640955456}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 19807, "create_time": 1640957282, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "中专生能教出些啥？", "timestamp": 1640957282}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 19808, "create_time": 1640957387, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "中专生自己也就只有这点智商，能教出什么名堂？认知就只有张美玉和那对部长水平，他们好歹没机会误人子弟", "timestamp": 1640957387}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 19809, "create_time": 1640957511, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 劝你别笑张美玉，只是一个再平凡不过的中国人罢了", "timestamp": 1640957511}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 19831, "create_time": 1640961494, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Alice: 学到了新词。我准备用它来形容西安的某些市民", "timestamp": 1640961494}], "create_time": 1640952670, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1640961494, "likenum": 7, "n_attentions": 7, "n_comments": 13, "pid": 6863, "poll": null, "reply": 13, "text": "很有感触，大国教育\n原来皇城教育方式和我们小县城也一样\nhttps://www.reddit.com/r/chonglangTV/comments/rsrmap/%E6%94%AF%E5%BC%8F%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2/", "timestamp": 1640952670}}